- HMM?

328
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,666
- I'M SORRY, AYEKA.

329
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:43,875
BUT I'M NOT THE REAL SASAMI!

330
00:16:43,958 --> 00:16:46,500
- HUH?

331
00:16:46,583 --> 00:16:49,250
WHAT-- WHAT DO YOU MEAN, SASAMI?

332
00:16:49,333 --> 00:16:51,375
WH-- WHAT?

333
00:16:51,458 --> 00:16:54,291
- ( crying )

334
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:58,875
- ( meows ) 

