00:16:58,958 --> 00:17:00,666
- SASAMI?

336
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:01,625
OH.

337
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,083
UH-HUH.

338
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:09,625
- 700 YEARS AGO.

339
00:17:09,708 --> 00:17:13,875
