00:18:43,625 --> 00:18:45,291
HOW DO YOU DO?

361
00:18:47,041 --> 00:18:48,958
( laughs )

362
00:18:54,125 --> 00:18:56,041
OH!

363
00:18:56,125 --> 00:18:59,875
OH!  AHHHH!

364
00:19:02,833 --> 00:19:05,708
( heartbeat )

365
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:49,041
- PRINCESS SASAMI!

366
00:19:49,125 --> 00:19:51,500
WHERE ARE YOU?

367
00:19:51,583 --> 00:19:53,166
OH, THERE YOU ARE!

368
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:55,166
- MAMA!

369
00:19:55,250 --> 00:19:58,083
- PRINCESS SASAMI!

370
00:19:58,166 --> 00:20:01,208
IS MY LITTLE PRINCESS ALL RIGHT?

371
00:20:01,291 --> 00:20:02,958
- YES!
- OH GOOD.

372
00:20:07,875 --> 00:20:12,375
- ( crying )
