374
00:20:15,791 --> 00:20:18,291
THEREFORE I AM--

375
00:20:18,375 --> 00:20:21,166
I AM NOT YOUR REAL SISTER!

376
00:20:21,250 --> 00:20:23,083
- HUH?

377
00:20:26,041 --> 00:20:28,375
- AYEKA!

378
00:20:28,458 --> 00:20:31,000
AYEKA!

379
00:20:33,208 --> 00:20:35,416
AYEKA!
PLEASE WAIT!

380
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:37,125
- ( laughs ) 

381
00:20:37,208 --> 00:20:39,708
- AYEKA, WAIT FOR ME!

382
00:20:39,791 --> 00:20:42,541
SISTER!
AYEKA, WAIT FOR ME!

383
00:20:42,625 --> 00:20:45,375
WAIT FOR ME!
- ( laughs ) 

384
00:20:45,458 --> 00:20:47,083
- AYEKA!

385
00:20:47,166 --> 00:20:48,500
- ( gasps )

