- ( giggling )

399
00:21:31,416 --> 00:21:32,625
REALLY?

400
00:21:32,708 --> 00:21:35,291
- YES, I DO!
YES, I DO!

401
00:21:35,375 --> 00:21:37,083
- YOU DO?

402
00:21:37,166 --> 00:21:38,833
WELL, I LOVE YOU TOO, SASAMI.

403
00:21:41,458 --> 00:21:43,958
WE LOVE EACH OTHER.
THAT'S WHAT COUNTS.

404
00:21:44,041 --> 00:21:45,708
- YES.

405
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:49,000
- WHOA!

406
00:21:49,083 --> 00:21:50,458
- TENCHI?

407
00:21:50,541 --> 00:21:53,666
- UM, UH, I--

408
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:56,125
- ( laughs ) 

409
00:21:56,208 --> 00:22:00,166
- I FEEL THE SAME
AS AYEKA.

410
00:22:00,250 --> 00:22:01,666
- AH.

411
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:04,708
- SASAMI, WE LIKE YOU
JUST THE WAY YOU ARE.

412
00:22:04,791 --> 00:22:06,291
- RIGHT.

413
00:22:06,375 --> 00:22:09,916
SASAMI, WHATEVER HAPPENS,
YOU ARE MY DEAR SISTER.

414
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,916
- AYEKA!

415
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,458
( sobbing )

416
00:22:15,958 --> 00:22:18,125
TENCHI!

417
00:22:18,208 --> 00:22:20,666
( sobbing )

418
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:24,041
- BE THAT WAY.
THAT'S FINE.

419
00:22:24,125 --> 00:22:26,291
- ( meows ) 
- ( laughs )

420
00:22:26,375 --> 00:22:28,500
SASAMI IS A LITTLE GIRL
AFTER ALL.

421
00:22:28,583 --> 00:22:32,500
LET'S SEE.
- ( muffled talking )

422
00:22:38,541 --> 00:22:41,416
- LOOKS LIKE
SHE'S FALLEN ASLEEP.

423
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:43,500
- YES, IT LOOKS THAT WAY.

