FOUND OUT ABOUT HER SECRET,

426
00:22:48,791 --> 00:22:50,250
WE WOULD LEAVE HER.

427
00:22:50,333 --> 00:22:54,083
SHE-- SHE TOLD ME
THAT THE REAL SASAMI DIED.

428
00:22:54,166 --> 00:22:56,875
BUT IF THAT'S TRUE, THEN--
- OH.

429
00:22:56,958 --> 00:22:58,416
- Tsunami: PRINCESS AYEKA?

430
00:23:07,208 --> 00:23:11,041
SASAMI DIDN'T REALLY DIE,
PRINCESS AYEKA.

431
00:23:11,125 --> 00:23:12,125
( gasps )

432
00:23:12,208 --> 00:23:14,416
- SHE THINKS OF HERSELF
AS MY CREATION.

433
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:17,666
BUT SHE ACTUALLY SURVIVED
BY ASSIMILATING WITH ME.

434
00:23:17,750 --> 00:23:22,375
SHE'S STILL YOUNG. ONE DAY
SHE WILL UNDERSTAND EVERYTHING.

435
00:23:22,458 --> 00:23:25,791
- I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL HER?

436
00:23:25,875 --> 00:23:28,625
- SHE WOULDN'T HAVE BELIEVED IT,
PRINCESS AYEKA,

437
00:23:28,708 --> 00:23:31,541
EVEN IF I HAD TOLD HER.

438
00:23:31,625 --> 00:23:35,875
BESIDES, SASAMI NEEDED TO KNOW
OF YOUR FEELINGS FOR HER.

439
00:23:35,958 --> 00:23:39,000
RIGHT NOW, THAT'S MORE IMPORTANT
THAN THE TRUTH OF HER IDENTITY.

440
00:23:39,083 --> 00:23:43,458
PRINCESS AYEKA, SHE TRULY IS
YOUR REAL SISTER.

441
00:23:54,333 --> 00:23:55,708
- WOW!

442
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,083
- BEAUTIFUL.

443
00:24:05,583 --> 00:24:07,875
- HERE YOU ARE.
