444
00:24:10,291 --> 00:24:14,166
AHH!
- ( all cheering )

445
00:24:14,250 --> 00:24:15,875
- BEAUTIFUL CHERRY BLOSSOMS.

446
00:24:15,958 --> 00:24:18,458
( laughs )
