455
00:24:38,291 --> 00:24:39,625
MMM!

456
00:24:39,708 --> 00:24:42,625
- YEEEE!  WHOOA!

457
00:24:47,291 --> 00:24:48,750
- OH NO.

458
00:24:57,666 --> 00:25:00,541
SOMEONE FEELING
KIND OF BLUE AROUND HERE?

459
00:25:00,625 --> 00:25:02,000
- MMM.

460
00:25:02,083 --> 00:25:03,500
- HMM.

461
00:25:03,583 --> 00:25:06,500
YOU KNOW, I DIDN'T KNOW
THAT JURAI HAD TREES

462
00:25:06,583 --> 00:25:08,916
THAT COULD TAKE ON HUMAN FORM.

463
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:11,166
( sighs )

464
00:25:11,250 --> 00:25:14,291
- YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND ANYTHING.

465
00:25:15,916 --> 00:25:17,750
- MEANING?

466
00:25:19,875 --> 00:25:23,250
- TSUNAMI AND SASAMI
ARE THE SAME.

467
00:25:23,333 --> 00:25:24,333
THERE-- GET IT?

468
00:25:24,416 --> 00:25:26,125
- SO WHAT?

469
00:25:27,458 --> 00:25:29,791
- WELL, THEY ARE ASSIMILATED.

470
00:25:29,875 --> 00:25:33,625
THAT MEANS THAT SASAMI
AND TSUNAMI ARE IDENTICAL.

471
00:25:33,708 --> 00:25:36,041
WHICH MEANS
THAT WHEN SASAMI GROWS UP...

472
00:25:36,125 --> 00:25:37,958
- SHE'LL LOOK LIKE TSUNAMI?

473
00:25:38,041 --> 00:25:40,333
HMM.  IT CAN'T BE.

474
00:25:40,416 --> 00:25:43,125
- Tsunami:
YES, SHE WILL BE LIKE ME.

475
00:25:48,208 --> 00:25:50,291
WE HAVE SEPARATE MINDS
RIGHT NOW,

476
00:25:50,375 --> 00:25:52,458
BUT WHEN WE ARE JOINED
IN ONE FORM...

477
00:25:53,916 --> 00:25:57,500
YOU CAN CALL ME SASAMI
OR TSUNAMI,

478
00:25:57,583 --> 00:25:59,666
WHICHEVER ONE YOU PREFER.

479
00:26:02,208 --> 00:26:03,333
- Both: HUH?

480
00:26:03,416 --> 00:26:06,083
- YOU NEEDN'T WORRY.

481
00:26:06,166 --> 00:26:09,750
WHEN WE ARE UNITED,
SHE WILL HAVE A COMPLETE MEMORY.

482
00:26:09,833 --> 00:26:12,750
- THAT'S NOT WHY WE'RE WORRIED.
- HUH?

483
00:26:12,833 --> 00:26:16,166
- SO SASAMI WILL LOOK LIKE YOU?

484
00:26:16,250 --> 00:26:19,625
- YES, I AM THE IMAGE
