487
00:26:24,083 --> 00:26:26,541
I THOUGHT SASAMI
WAS NOTHING TO WORRY ABOUT.

488
00:26:26,625 --> 00:26:28,541
- I DIDN'T PLAN ON THIS.

489
00:26:28,625 --> 00:26:30,916
SASAMI'S BEAUTY
WILL SURPASS MINE.

490
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,708
- ( both grunting )

491
00:26:32,791 --> 00:26:36,958
- WELL, SHE'S A LOT PRETTIER
THAN YOU ARE.  HMM!

492
00:26:37,041 --> 00:26:40,208
- AND AT LEAST SHE'S BETTER
LOOKING THAN YOU ARE.

493
00:26:40,291 --> 00:26:41,625
- WHAT'D YOU SAY?

494
00:26:41,708 --> 00:26:43,291
