- Ayeka: WHAT DO YOU THINK,
YOU SIMPLETON?

510
00:27:26,666 --> 00:27:28,750
- Mihoshi:
OH, I'M SO SORRY.

511
00:27:28,833 --> 00:27:30,916
- Ryoko:
I'M GONNA GET YOU!

512
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,666
- Mihoshi: AHHH!

513
00:27:32,750 --> 00:27:34,375
- ( splashing )

514
00:27:37,458 --> 00:27:40,416
- ( theme music playing )

515
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:48,750
♪ I AM LONELY
